------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README
Directory:  ./hog 

@author dharabor
@created 2016-05-02
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains a modified version of Nathan Sturtevant's pathfinding
library Hierarchical Open Graph (HOG).  In the period 2009-2011 I used HOG as
a development testbed for the algorithms known as Jump Point Search and
Rectangular Symmetry Reduction. 

Please note:
The implementations found here are **VERY OLD** AND **NOT VERY OPTIMISED**
They are no longer maintained.

More recent implementations and extensions of Jump Point Search can be found 
as part of the Warthog pathfinding library (see directory ./src).

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compilation notes
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
make

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Running the program
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./bin/hog 

Executing the program without any arguments will cause it to print usage 
instructions.  The program can be run in with or without a GUI.


